introduction of schools--

00:03:15.870 --> 00:03:19.560
academies and schools into
the Middle East, the first one

00:03:19.560 --> 00:03:22.400
having been founded
in 1908 in Egypt--

00:03:22.400 --> 00:03:24.330
there was a young
prince from Egypt.

00:03:24.330 --> 00:03:27.284
He was the nephew of the king,
and he wanted to study art.

00:03:27.284 --> 00:03:28.200
And he couldn't leave.

00:03:28.200 --> 00:03:30.366
So they opened an academy
for him, which is amazing.

00:03:30.366 --> 00:03:31.020
[LAUGHTER]

